  "text": "In the case of an attempt to engage nonviolently with a locally based group linked to Al-Qaeda while its transnational leadership remains opposed to any such engagement, this would mean treating the latter as a spoiler [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . According to Stedman's framework, a spoiler is a group that seeks to undermine a peace process.",
