      "title": "Spoiler Problems in Peace Processes",
      "abstract": "An animal exercising observatory which includes a hollow transparent sphere in which an animal may exercise for causing translatory rolling of the sphere along an external surface in contact therewith, the animal remaining continuously observable. The sphere includes a door which in contour is complemental to the sphere for permitting access into the latter."
